Try to define virtual interface which overwrite the parameter in the test regression t_interface_parameter_access.v. 

    virtual test_if#(.FOO(identity(5))) the_vif;

    test_if #( .FOO (identity(5)) ) the_interface ();
    test_if #( .FOO (identity(7)) ) array_interface [1:0] ();

run `verilator t_interface_parameter_access.v --cc` and I got error as below

    $ verilator t_interface_parameter_access.v --cc
    %Error: Internal Error: t_interface_parameter_access.v:39:23: ../V3LinkDot.cpp:2247: Pin not under instance?
       39 |     virtual test_if#(.FOO(identity(5))) the_vif;
          |                       ^~~
                            ... See the manual at https://verilator.org/verilator_doc.html for more assistance.

 I am using `Verilator 5.006 2023-01-22 rev UNKNOWN.REV`
